OL,6,FVasectomies are to be carried out by
OL,7,FGPs in Northern Ireland rather than in
OL,8,Fhospitals, Health Minister Robin Swann
OL,9,Fhas announced.
OL,11,FMr Swann said he believed the
OL,12,Fdecision, which will begin to take
OL,13,Feffect immediately, will result in
OL,14,Fhundreds more procedures on men being
OL,15,Fcarried out in the first year.
OL,17,FIt will involve around #450,000 per
OL,18,Fyear being re-allocated to primary
OL,19,Fcare.
