OL,6,FMr Swann's funding announcement means
OL,7,Fthere will be a transition phase for
OL,8,Fservices throughout 2024/25, and from
OL,9,F2025/26 onwards, GPs will be the sole
OL,10,Fprovider of health service vasectomy
OL,11,Fservices.
OL,13,FScalpel-free vasectomies have been
OL,14,Fprovided by GPs in recent years
OL,15,Fthrough the primary care elective care
OL,16,Fservice.
OL,18,FFunding, however, had been on a non-
OL,19,Frecurrent basis and was not provided
OL,20,Ffor the second half of 2023/24 due to
OL,21,Fhealth service budgetary pressures.
