OL,6,FAbout 1,000 patients are currently on
OL,7,Fhospital waiting lists for the
OL,8,Fprocedure.
OL,10,FMr Swann said: "My decision will
OL,11,Fensure a more localised service for
OL,12,Fpatients, and I am confident it will
OL,13,Fresult in hundreds more procedures
OL,14,Fbeing provided in the first year alone.
OL,16,F"This innovation is a positive example
OL,17,Fof services being relocated for the
OL,18,Fbenefit of patients ` and with lower
OL,19,Fcosts per procedure."
