OL,6,FDr Joe Devlin, clinical director for
OL,7,Fthe Primary Care Vasectomy Service,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have been providing a high
OL,9,Fquality, easily accessible, cost-
OL,10,Feffective vasectomy service in primary
OL,11,Fcare for several years now.
OL,13,F"The announcement by the minister
OL,14,Ftoday provides long-term security for
OL,15,Fthe future of the service, allowing us
OL,16,Fto plan more effectively to deliver
OL,17,Fand develop the service.
