OL,6,F"It is a welcome vote of confidence in
OL,7,Fprimary care that it can be the main
OL,8,Fprovider of important services like
OL,9,Fthis."
OL,11,FDr Ursula Mason, a GP in Carryduff and
OL,12,Fchair of the Royal College of GPs
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland, said: "We know that
OL,14,Fthe suspension of this vital service
OL,15,Flast October caused a lot of worry for
OL,16,Fpeople across our communities.
