OL,6,FShe added: "This investment in GP
OL,7,Fvasectomy services is an example of
OL,8,Ftransformation in action, allowing
OL,9,Fpatients who would otherwise have been
OL,10,Flanguishing on prohibitively long
OL,11,Fwaiting lists in secondary care to be
OL,12,Fable to be treated more quickly, at an
OL,13,Faffordable cost, closer to home.
OL,15,F"This announcement is testament to
OL,16,Fwhat is possible with a functioning
OL,17,FExecutive and minister who is willing
OL,18,Fto take robust decisions which will
OL,19,Fbenefit patients in the long-term.
